<td>The ID of the post to delete</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='get-post-39-s-responses'>Get Post&#39;s Responses</h2><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://community.tribe.so/api/v1/posts/5c0621864cb2b119dc174a63/responses"</span>
