<h2 id='update-a-specific-comment-for-a-specific-post'>Update a Specific Comment for a Specific Post</h2><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>  curl <span class="s2">"https://community.tribe.so/api/v1/posts/5bf0e89ada3be54c190b78ba/comments/4sf0e89ada3be54c190b78b2"</span>
